'''Nadia Chafik''' {{Tifinaɣ|'''ⵏⴰⴷⵢⴰ ⵛⴰⴼⵉⵇ'''}}


Tlul '''Nadia Cafik''' ɣ-ussggas n 1962 ɣ [[Tigmmi Tumlilt]] ɣ tamurt n [[Amṛṛuk|Umrruk]] tili ɣ tfilit n timɣarin n lislam tusna.<ref>Suad Joseph, Afsaneh Najmabadi, ''Encyclopedia of Women & Islamic Cultures'', ed. Brill, 2003, ISBN 9789004128217, p.24</ref>
Cafik tuder ɣ tamurt Lmrruk. Ar tssaqra tutlayt n tafransist d umyawaḍ ɣ faculti n  [[Luniversiti Mohammed V]] n [[Ṛbaṭ|Rbat]]. Tsni mnnaw idlisn. iligesn Adllis n  "Nos jours aveugles" (Ussa neɣ ibukaḍn) ig yan  ɣ idllisens imzyura  ɣ talɣa nu umzruy.
Tg '''Nadia Chafik''' yat ɣ timɣarin timrrukay li ittaran s tafransist, d yat li icnubucn ɣ umzruy Lmrruk, taws ad adsen midn amzruyad li ukan zul iḥban , d liɣ sul ukan illa ma baḥra ittuynnan.
